movies.description: The Exorcism tells the story of Anthony Miller, an actor who starts acting strangely while working on a horror movie. His daughter Lee notices his odd behavior and fears something evil might be involved. As things get worse, Lee teams up with a priest to save her father from a dark force. The battle against the demon pushes them to their limits, leading to a dramatic exorcism. It's a story about family, faith, and fighting against evil.

The Conjuring follows Ed and Lorraine Warren, paranormal investigators, as they help the Perron family, who are haunted by dark forces in their new farmhouse. Strange events escalate, and the Warrens discover the house is cursed by an evil spirit named Bathsheba. The spirit possesses the mother, Carolyn, and attempts to harm the family. With faith and determination, the Warrens perform an exorcism to save Carolyn and defeat the spirit, restoring peace to the family.

A cursed videotape causes anyone who watches it to die seven days later. Journalist Rachel investigates the mysterious deaths linked to the tape and uncovers the tragic story of Samara, a girl with psychic abilities who was killed by her mother. Rachel discovers the way to survive is by copying the tape and showing it to someone else. The cycle of horror continues as she grapples with the consequences of her actions..

On Halloween night in 1963, six-year-old Michael Myers murders his sister and is institutionalized. Fifteen years later, he escapes and returns to his hometown of Haddonfield to stalk and kill teenagers, including babysitter Laurie Strode. As his psychiatrist Dr. Loomis hunts him, Michael methodically targets his victims with relentless precision. Laurie fights back, narrowly surviving multiple attacks. The film ends with Michael mysteriously vanishing after being shot, leaving his evil presence lingering.
True-crime writer Ellison Oswalt discovers a box of home movies that put his family in great danger as he uncovers a supernatural force tied to the horrific events.
A family looks to prevent evil spirits from trapping their comatose child in a realm called The Further.
A group of bullied kids band together when a monster, taking the appearance of a clown, begins hunting children.
A group of friends visit a deserted colony, only to experience supernatural horrors. The horror intensifies as they uncover the dark secrets of the place.
A woman seeks revenge against those who wronged her and her family, as she becomes involved in a chilling series of supernatural events.
A couple begins to experience terrifying events when they are gifted a vintage doll that is possessed by an evil spirit.
A group of people survive a deadly accident after a series of premonitions, but they soon realize that Death itself is coming after them one by one.
In a post-apocalyptic world, a family is forced to live in silence while hiding from monsters with ultra-sensitive hearing.

details.producer: Michael Bay, Andrew Form, Brad Fuller

movies.description: A supernatural horror thriller about a struggling single mother who becomes entangled in the haunting mysteries surrounding an abandoned movie theater.
A chilling dive into the mind of a disturbed individual, exploring themes of madness, brutality, and the terrifying depths of human depravity.
A family inherits a luxurious glass mansion, unaware that it houses vengeful spirits and a deadly secret.
A horrifying tale of three filmmakers who venture into Ukraine to document the story of a cannibalistic spirit.
A chilling story of a family terrorized by paranormal forces in their new home, based on real-life events.
The Warrens travel to north London to help a single mother whose children are being tormented by an angry spirit.
A social worker and her children are drawn into a frightening supernatural world when a troubled mother is accused of child endangerment and haunted by the ghostly figure of La Llorona.
A young girl is left alone with her siblings and is drawn into a terrifying world after using a Ouija board to contact her deceased father, unleashing a malevolent force.
A journalist investigates a case of a nun's death, leading her to uncover terrifying truths about an alleged demonic possession.
The prequel to Annabelle, revealing the origin of the possessed doll as a group of orphans and a nun become its victims.
A grieving mother battles her son's fear of a monster lurking in their home, only to discover a sinister presence is haunting them.
A young woman becomes involved in a terrifying curse after investigating a house where a supernatural entity resides.
A group of teenagers is stalked by a masked killer who targets them based on horror movie tropes. As they try to uncover the identity of the killer, they must confront their worst fears.
